data.description: Great potential in this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offering 1,397 sqft of space! Upon entering the home is the large living space with high ceilings and a brick, wood burning fireplace. Following into the kitchen there is a breakfast/dining area, ample cabinet space, dishwasher, electric stove, and a peek through window opening to the living room! The spacious master suite offers a private bathroom, with a single vanity and shower/tub combo. Enjoy the space the backyard has to offer with a covered patio and privacy fencing. Home is being sold as-is, but the sellers are also offering a $5,000 allowance! Don't miss this great opportunity!
